### 5. Form Validation (Zod) ✅

**Schema:**
```typescript
{
  title: 10-200 chars (required)
  topic: 5+ chars (required)
  kind: enum (article|email|social_script|ad_copy)
  tone: enum (5 options)
  audience: optional string
  body: 100+ chars (optional in draft, required for publish)
}
```

**Validation Features:**
- ✅ Runtime validation before submission
- ✅ Clear error messages
- ✅ Field-level validation
- ✅ Type-safe form data

